text: Cemal Yanılmaz (2 January 1934 - 6 June 2018) is a Turkish wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle flyweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1934 births Category:2018 deaths Category:Turkish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Turkey Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics
